<p>LET\'S GET STARTED!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>WHAT IS FOREX TRADING?</strong></p>
<p>Forex is just a Short form for&nbsp;<strong>FOREIGN EXCHANGE</strong>.</p>
<p>The foreign exchange&nbsp; (Forex, FX, or currency market is a global decentralized or Over-The-Counter (OTC) market for the the rading of international currencies such Euros, dollars, pounds, Japanese yen etc. For profit maximization.&nbsp;</p>
<p>In layman&rsquo;s terms, FX trading is the act of buying one currency while selling another simultaneously. Currency values are constantly shifting. They can either be rising in value(appreciating) or decreasing in value(depreciating) due to a number of reasons such as economics and politics. The entire goal of people involved in the Foreign Exchange market is to take advantage of these changes and profit from them.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Unlike most other financial markets, Forex trading can occur 24-hours a day though a global network of businesses, banks and individuals. This means you could be making money even while you sleep. And what&rsquo;s wrong with that?&nbsp;The Online Forex market has great potentials and there are countless numbers of opportunities that come with forex trading.</p>
<p>Forex is one of the largest market in the world with a Total Daily Liquidity of $5.3 Trillion dollars. It is larger than New York Stock Exchange market and the Cryptomarket combined together.</p>
<p><strong>MAJOR PARTICIPANTS IN THE FOREX MARKET</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Central Banks</li>
<li>Banks</li>
<li>Corporations</li>
<li>Retail Traders</li>
</ul>',
